{"tid":1361547,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣請入: 義士翻譯為Patriots","createTime":"2019-07-24T15:35:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T17:29:18.000Z","uid":276716,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"87ea3f82eb42d6efbadfab092d1746fbc0e02577","tid":1361547,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:35:30.000Z","msg":"文宣手足， &ldquo;義士&rdquo;一路冇統一嘅英文翻譯，不利於海外文宣。小弟不才，建議用Patriots稱呼義士。<br />\n字典解釋Patriot: <br />\na person who vigorously supports their country and is prepared to defend it against enemies or detractors.<br />\n非常準確描述到義士嘅精神，不多不少，恰到好處。<br />\n<br />\n有其他譯法，例如martyr, righteous, comrade，但我覺得各有不妥之處。<br />\n<br />\nMartyr通常係形容死咗嘅烈士，但目前未有人因為示威而被殺或者受嚴重虐待，所以唔建議用呢個字，否則萬一將來情況再惡化，我地修辭就冇得再升級。好似政府day 1就用咗暴動，依家就冇字可用。我地唔好犯同一個錯。<br />\n<br />\nRighteous 有morally right嘅意思，對義士嚟講太沉重。義士都係凡人，有軟弱嘅時候，我地唔可以期望義士係不食人間煙火嘅聖人。<br />\n<br />\nComrade 畀共產黨用得太多，就不詳述了。"},{"pid":"2c807150f01d6aca6ebd1a2a3d6629eee1d6de8b","tid":1361547,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:41:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好撚重要！唔該幫手推啊！！推得好辛苦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【唔想輸嘅入嚟幫手置頂】如何避免被人鳩帶風向+攻破白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361315</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"63f25bb5c32d3b3973264e69c9b1f32416a78075","tid":1361547,"uid":67645,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:43:18.000Z","msg":"翻做patriots會唔會易令外國人誤會？<br />\n因為客觀上睇好多外國人都仲覺得香港係中國一部分<br />\n會唔會令人以為係愛中國份子？<br />\n<br />\n反而由「義士」嘅用法開始諗會好啲？<br />\n我地講義士唔係指道德上嘅「義」<br />\n更加似講緊「勇敢嘅反抗者」<br />\n由語意上諗應該更好"},{"pid":"5aab668ab9f27f6571c7c669bc96510966030850","tid":1361547,"uid":48729,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:53:31.000Z","msg":"我覺得香港嘅義士本質上係 patriotic，大家都係忠於自己嘅土地，為香港去盡力。問題係太易俾人誤解做「愛中國」，然後就會亂到九彩。<br />\n再諗諗其他叫法。"},{"pid":"108aa9b435d5bec4db3042df71c467f835df2868","tid":1361547,"uid":278723,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:53:42.000Z","msg":"Patriots是解為愛國者"},{"pid":"5df75f08baaef57c1e1a4e0e7f2b2e813f4c7157","tid":1361547,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:06:09.000Z","msg":"英國世界中，香港係一個country。等如Scotland, Wales 都係country。"},{"pid":"f40975d9f211f9e3889431a8fbf8727ae58da8b1","tid":1361547,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5df75f08baaef57c1e1a4e0e7f2b2e813f4c7157","tid":1361547,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:06:09.000Z","msg":"英國世界中，香港係一個country。等如Scotland, Wales 都係country。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:07:54.000Z","msg":"英<span style=\"color: red;\">語</span>世界"},{"pid":"199f8524fdcbb4e0ac8f108c54e7baa7b0bd5104","tid":1361547,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arQuwcJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarQuwcJ.png&h=02d40e21&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}